an-Francois.Bernardet @ jouy.inra.fr</p>\n  <p><b>Richard J. Birtles,</b> School of Environment and Life Sciences, Peel Building, University of Salford, Salford, Greater Manchester M5 4WT, UK</p>\n  <p>Fax: +44 161 295 5726; e-mail: r.j.birtles @ salford.ac.uk</p>\n  <p><b>John Bowman,</b> School of Agricultural Science, University of Tasmania, GPO Box 252-54, Hobart 7001, Tasmania, Australia</p>\n  <p>Fax: +61 3 6226 2642; e-mail: john.bowman @ utas.edu.au</p>\n  <p><b>Hans-Jürgen Busse,</b> Institut für Bakteriology, Mykology und Hygiene, Veterinärmedizinische Universität Wien, Veterinärplatz 1, A-1210 Wien, Austria</p>\n  <p>Fax: +43 1 250 77 2190; e-mail: hans-juergen.busse @ vu-wien.ac.at</p>\n  <p><b>Jang-Cheon Cho,</b> Division of Biology and Ocean Sciences, Inha University, Yonghyun dong 253, Incheon 402-751, Republic of Korea</p>\n  <p>Fax: +82 32 232 0541; e-mail: chojc @ inha.ac.kr</p>\n  <p><b>Henrik Christensen,</b> Department of Veterinary Pathobiology, Center for Applied Bioinformatics, Life Science, Veterinary Medicine, Copenhagen University, Dyrlægevej 88, DK-1870 Frederiksberg C, Denmark</p>\n  <p>Fax: +45 353 32 757; e-mail: hech @ life.ku.dk</p>\n  <p><b>Jongsik Chun,</b> School of Biological Sciences, Seoul National University, 56-1 Shillim-Dong, Kwanak-gu, Seoul 151-742, Republic of Korea</p>\n  <p>Fax: +82 2 888 4911; e-mail: jchun @ snu.ac.kr</p>\n  <p><b>Micah Dunthorn,</b> University of Kaiserslautern, Department of Ecology, Erwin-Schroedinger Street, 67653 Kaiserslautern, Germany</p>\n  <p>Fax: +49 0631 205 2496; e-mail: dunthorn @ rhrk.uni-kl.de</p>\n  <p><b>Christian Hertel,</b> German Institute of Food Technologies (DIL), Professor-von-Klitzing-Straße 7, D-49610 Quakenbrück, Germany</p>\n  <p>Fax: +49 5431 183114; e-mail: c.hertel @ dil-ev.de</p>\n  <p><b>David P. Labeda,</b> Microbial Properties Research, National Center for Agricultural Utilization Research, Agricultural Research Service, US Department of Agriculture, Peoria, IL 61604